# 🛠️ How to Run Locally

### 1. Clone the repository
```sh
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/YOUR_REPO_NAME.git
cd ezcirkit-store
````

### 2. Install dependencies

```sh
npm install
```

### 3. Add environment variables

Create a `.env.local` file:

```
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=<your-supabase-url>
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=<your-anon-key>

RAZORPAY_KEY_ID=<your-razorpay-key>
RAZORPAY_KEY_SECRET=<your-razorpay-secret>
```

### 4. Run the project

```sh
npm run dev
```

---

# 💰 Payments (Razorpay Flow)

1. User fills checkout form
2. `/payment` loads total
3. Creates Razorpay order ID
4. Opens Razorpay widget
5. On success → verify signature
6. Save order in Supabase
7. Redirect to `/success`

---

# 🚀 Deployment

During deployment:

1. Push to GitHub
2. Connect repo to Vercel
3. Add same `.env.local` values in Vercel Environment Variables
4. Deploy
5. Add domain: `ezcirkit.crabstertech.in`

